para.text: The collected mist passes through the primary filter and is separated by centrifugal force generated by the rotating drum filter. Oil droplets will form on the walls of the housing and exit out through the discharge ports. The clean air is then passed through the drum filter and is discharged from the air discharge outlet. The cutting fluid is returned to the machining chamber.
